NetSIPServer

The NetSIPServer is a Server to connect SIP Phones to this Server.

  • C# (3.5)

  • Microsoft SQL Server 2008

  • Microsoft Visual Studio 2008
  • Microsoft Silverlight
  • Microsoft ASP.NET (3.5)
  • Office Communications Server (OCS)
  • Windows PowerShell
